
**arrived at by a practising yogi by renunciation being appraised of the supreme knowledge that the material world is false this stage can only be acquired by those who attain super natural illumination without the aid of physical or mental organs**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   நிருவிகற்பமாதல்
